jsx updated\\n- Frontend: Vite + React + Ant Design + Redux\\n- Backend: Express + TypeORM + MongoDB\\n\\n### Infrastructure Setup\\n- Frontend dev server: port 3002 → http://103.253.21.139:3002\\n- Backend: port 5555 → http://103.253.21.139:5555\\n- MongoDB: port 27017 (Docker, image mongo:7)\\n- Vite proxy configured: `/api` → `http://localhost:5555`\\n- Frontend .env: VITE_PORT=3002, VITE_API_SERVER= (empty → relative URLs via proxy)\\n- B\\n\\nSource: memory/2026-04-20.md#L66-L95\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"citation\": \"memory/2026-04-20.md#L66-L95\",\n      \"corpus\": \"memory\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"31578122c0d057edd08907b2fb80a1586c0c68091ea7d962dfb45fefd39331b7\",\n      \"path\": \"memory/2026-04-20.md\",\n      \"startLine\": 20,\n      \"endLine\": 54,\n      \"score\": 0.6371025617860743,\n      \"textScore\": 0.6371025617860743,\n      \"snippet\": \"- Components created: StatsRow.jsx, CalendarSection.jsx, CostTable.jsx, DriverInfo.jsx\\n- Dashboard chart/index.jsx updated\\n- Frontend: Vite + React + Ant Design + Redux\\n- Backend: Express + TypeORM + MongoDB\\n\\n### Infrastructure Setup\\n- Frontend dev server: port 3002 → http://103.253.21.139:3002\\n- Backend: port 5555 → http://103.253.21.139:5555\\n- MongoDB: port 27017 (Docker, image mongo:7)\\n- Vite proxy configured: `/api` → `http://localhost:5555`\\n- Frontend .env: VITE_PORT=3002, VITE_API_SERVER= (empty → relative URLs via proxy)\\n- Backend CORS fixed: changed `origin: '*'` → `origin: ['http://localhost:3000', 'http://103.253.21.139:3002', 'http://localhost:3002']`\\n\\n### Auth Status\\n- Backend AP\\n\\nSource: memory/2026-04-20.md#L20-L54\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"citation\": \"memory/2026-04-20.md#L20-L54\",\n      \"corpus\": \"memory\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"7bf314a7b47cd40bb7203df8fc6d9a64efdee8aa26972ae0be8ebf0ad43bed1a\",\n      \"path\": \"memory/2026-04-19-1809.md\",\n      \"startLine\": 1,\n      \"endLine\": 6,\n      \"sc