{"type":"message","id":"10b02319","parentId":"adffc9cc","timestamp":"2026-04-21T07:41:28.892Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"No confluence env vars in the systemd service file. This is the issue! The systemd service doesn't have the Confluence env vars set. The env vars are only in the openclaw.json config, but the confluence MCP server needs them as environment variables to connect to Confluence.\n\nLet me update the systemd service to include the confluence env vars.","thinkingSignature":"a1daf877613d19a0c4a64373c71b3397efeb73318bea590b2ab87d9a00db42c9"},{"type":"text","text":"Thiếu env vars trong systemd! Fix ngay:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_tw03a6jikatp_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/update_service.py","content":"import json\n\n# Read current service\nwith open('/tmp/fix_service.sh', 'w') as f:\n    f.write('''#!/bin/bash\ncat > /etc/systemd/system/openclaw-gateway.service << 'EOF'\n[Unit]\nDescription=OpenClaw Gateway\nAfter=network.target\n\n[Service]\nType=simple\nUser=root\nWorkingDirectory=/root/.openclaw\nEnvironment=\"AHVHOLDING_API_KEY=sk-3d8edc47e4037bc4-en4js2-0a5bcb88\"\nEnvironment=\"PATH=/usr/bin:/usr/local/sbin:/usr/local/bin:/usr/sbin:/usr/bin:/sbin:/bin\"\nEnvironment=\"CONFLUENCE_URL=https://dtlx.atlassian.net/wiki/home\"\nEnvironment=\"CONFLUENCE_EMAIL=trandienxuan@gmail.com\"\nEnvironment=\"CONFLUENCE_TOKEN=ATATT3xFfGF0JFeb75S7LGrBWhi7SJ6t99S2ym8gMKQOFRvE0jT1gRanHowXdbPh82YFyDzf6T2oWGEBEuRko0-6lNu70_ZXev0hPtnwLg--S977t5bT9A_bA5_6gzmhTLb3Y0HS019TL8DWIBTxrUuKv3X8V_ZvJ--fODEEp2GyCxe35hkN6rU=CCD757BD\"\nExecStart=/usr/bin/openclaw gateway --port 18789\nRestart=always\nRestartSec=10\nStandardOutput=journal\nStandardOutput=journal\nStandardError=journal\n\n[Install]\nWantedBy=multi-user.target\nEOF\n''')\nprint('Done')\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":100,"output":494,"cacheRead":65431,"cacheWrite":269,"totalToken