{"type":"message","id":"7861ac74","parentId":"e92f0b41","timestamp":"2026-04-21T08:11:12.020Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I see the problem. The config has invalid keys:\n1. `agents.defaults.subagents.allowAgents` - unrecognized key\n2. `agents.defaults.skills` - unrecognized key\n\nThese are in the `agents.defaults` section. The VPS version is 2026.4.15 and doesn't support these keys in `agents.defaults`. I need to remove these keys from the config.Let me fix the config by removing the invalid keys from agents.defaults.","thinkingSignature":"5d66a3a742f2a831dc43a45d25ce365450c11cea86178117b1c4d8b0529788b6"},{"type":"text","text":"Thấy vấn đề rồi! Config có keys không tương thích:\n- `agents.defaults.subagents.allowAgents` ❌\n- `agents.defaults.skills` ❌\n\nFix:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_0gzose3zr8g7_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/fix_config.py","content":"import json\n\nwith open('/root/.openclaw/openclaw.json', 'r') as f:\n    config = json.load(f)\n\n# Remove incompatible keys from agents.defaults\ndefaults = config.get('agents', {}).get('defaults', {})\ndefaults.pop('subagents', None)\ndefaults.pop('skills', None)\n\nwith open('/root/.openclaw/openclaw.json', 'w') as f:\n    json.dump(config, f, indent=2)\n\nprint('Fixed. defaults now:', json.dumps(config.get('agents',{}).get('defaults',{})))\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":764,"output":302,"cacheRead":82289,"cacheWrite":252,"totalTokens":83607,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776759063326,"responseId":"063664186435b0eb0389cce9d71bc808"}}
