{"type":"message","id":"4171ab5c","parentId":"9f1e2686","timestamp":"2026-04-21T08:35:52.003Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"5412\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"6053576134\",\n  \"sender\": \"Khương Nịnh\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-04-21 08:35 UTC\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Khương Nịnh (6053576134)\",\n  \"id\": \"6053576134\",\n  \"name\": \"Khương Nịnh\",\n  \"username\": \"khuowgn\"\n}\n```\n\nấy lưu ý là phần config liên quan đến cronJob mà tạo công việc như đăng bài, tạo video xoá cho tôi nhé không được cho các vps khác sử dụng cả các agent deep-research, documentation-lookup, content-engine, article-writing,"}],"timestamp":1776760551985}}
{"type":"message","id":"1a39a033","parentId":"4171ab5c","timestamp":"2026-04-21T08:36:16.012Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to:\n1. Remove/disable CRON-related config on remote VPSs (posting jobs, video creation, etc.)\n2. Remove these agents from remote VPSs: deep-research, documentation-lookup, content-engine, article-writing\n\nLet me think about this:\n1. Cron jobs are stored in `/root/.openclaw/cron/jobs.json` - I should clear this or ensure no cron jobs exist on remote VPSs\n2. For the agents - should I remove them entirely from the workspace directories and from openclaw.json agents list? Or just disable them?\n\nThe user said \"xoá\" (delete) for content-engine and article-writing agents, and mentioned \"xoá cho tôi\" (delete for me) regarding cron jobs. \n\nSo the distinction is clear: those four agents should be completely removed from both the workspace directories and the openclaw.json configuration on the remote VPSs, while cron jobs need to be wiped entirely from the jobs.json file.","thinkingSignature":"5b81bcc55fe3ee3a4807937263b301b100c734ac86e40e0d85af19227da65b12"},{"type":"text","text":"Hiểu rồi! Xóa cron jobs + xóa 4 agents trên cả 2 VPS remote:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_x8dcp8uodfol_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/cleanup_cron_agents.sh","content":"#!/bin/bash\n# 1. Clear all cron jobs\necho \"=== Cron jobs ===\"\ncat /root/.openclaw/cron/jobs.json 2>/dev/null || echo \"no file\"\necho '{\"jobs\":[]}' > /root/.openclaw/cron/jobs.json\necho \"Cron cleared.\"\n\n# 2. Delete specific agent workspaces\necho \"=== Deleting agent workspaces ===\"\nfor agent in deep-research documentation-lookup content-engine article-writing; do\n    if [ -d \"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/$agent\" ]; then\n        rm -rf \"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/$agent\"\n        echo \"Deleted workspace: $agent\"\n    fi\ndone\n\n# 3. Remove from openclaw.json agents list\npython3 << 'PYEOF'\nimport json\n\nwith open('/root/.openclaw/openclaw.json', 'r') as f:\n    config = json.load(f)\n\nagents_to_remove = ['deep-research', 'documentation-lookup', 'content-engine', 'article-writing']\n\n# Remove from agents.list\nagent_list = config.get('agents', {}).get('list', [])\nbefore = len(agent_list)\nconfig['agents']['list'] = [a for a in agent_list if a.get('id') not in agents_to_remove]\nafter = len(config['agents']['list'])\n\nwith open('/root/.openclaw/openclaw.json', 'w') as f:\n    json.dump(config, f, indent=2)\n\nprint(f\"Agents: {before} -> {after} (removed {before - after})\")\nPYEOF\n\necho \"=== Done ===\"\nls /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/ | wc -l\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":267,"output":637,"cacheRead":96107,"cacheWrite":144,"totalTokens":97155,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776760552004,"responseId":"063669ea6556fb22fa2783942f869ca7"}}
