{"type":"message","id":"51308a43","parentId":"159a5075","timestamp":"2026-04-21T08:47:40.117Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see. The `models.json` file has the API key for each provider. Each VPS has a different API key:\n- VPS 140: `sk-3d8edc47e4037bc4-en4js2-0a5bcb88`\n- VPS 141: `sk-3d8edc47e4037bc4-8cqz7x-9e68394f`\n- Local: `sk-3d8edc47e4037bc4-w85g8t-b82baf0b`\n\n\nI need to update the API key in all the `models.json` files across both VPS. Since there are roughly 40 agents, I'll need to write a script that can handle this efficiently across all of them.","thinkingSignature":"e6f77629e1d9f2acd626f444013ac81b156db67bf2ff3bd04242ed323fd450ff"},{"type":"text","text":"Cần update API key trong `models.json` của mỗi agent. Viết script:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_lvmag40lisov_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls /root/.openclaw/agents/*/agent/models.json 2>/dev/null | wc -l","timeout":10}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":0,"output":240,"cacheRead":105435,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":105675,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776761251422,"responseId":"06366ca5d2df26edb79cbe8993527ab1"}}
