{"type":"message","id":"43d708fe","parentId":"5ca38cf8","timestamp":"2026-04-21T08:47:49.965Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"44 models.json files. Let me write a script that replaces the API key in all of them. The API key in models.json is different per VPS:- VPS 141: `sk-3d8edc47e4037bc4-8cqz7x-9e68394f`\n- VPS 140: `sk-3d8edc47e4037bc4-en4js2-0a5bcb88`\n\nI'll need to replace the old API key pattern. But wait - the old key in models.json is `sk-3d8edc47e4037bc4-uqgure-3230ee14` on the local machine. \n\nSo I need to generate scripts for both VPS that will swap out this old API key with the correct one for each environment.","thinkingSignature":"270dbb23667e173916c0e5181814ea3961b4e06351be46e6bcb5685b2285ee92"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_44c8ltlfax9t_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/fix_models141.sh","content":"#!/bin/bash\n# Update API key in all models.json files\nfind /root/.openclaw/agents -name 'models.json' -exec sed -i 's/sk-3d8edc47e4037bc4-[a-z0-9-]*/sk-3d8edc47e4037bc4-8cqz7x-9e68394f/g' {} \\;\necho \"Done. Verifying...\"\ngrep -r \"sk-3d8edc47e4037bc4-8cqz7x-9e68394f\" /root/.openclaw/agents/*/agent/models.json | wc -l\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":79,"output":349,"cacheRead":105048,"cacheWrite":565,"totalTokens":106041,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776761260223,"responseId":"06366cadd90c116200e8437db4239881"}}
