{"type":"message","id":"9308a57b","parentId":"2788b7d6","timestamp":"2026-04-21T09:28:23.398Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see the issue! The `channels.telegram.botToken` in the config is different from the main bot token. It has `allowFrom: [8255051109]` which is a different user ID (not Khương Nịnh's 6053576134). \n\nThe `main-bot` account token would be in the `channels` section. Let me check if there's a `main-bot` specific configuration. The user might be referring to the Telegram bot token that was supposed to be set as `telegram.botToken` — which on VPS 140 should be `8644096400:AAG_AqRTg-KtsWKl0EmhnpveJ4RjtMWmiVg`.\n\n\nThe config still shows the old token `8719830796:AAEjLcIHJskZnqZdwYf_V4bDWkAgP7C1YX0` instead of the new one I updated earlier. I only modified `env.TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN`, but the actual bot token the system uses comes from `channels.telegram.botToken`, so I need to update that field instead.","thinkingSignature":"4e9dd99dccbf48f821a7eb3964b17fd7ebbe7569c2b31b7a377b1ae509213ba8"},{"type":"text","text":"Thấy vấn đề! Có 2 nơi lưu Telegram token:\n- `env.TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN` ✅ (đã update)\n- `channels.telegram.botToken` ❌ (vẫn là token cũ)\n\nFix:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_05d9bx857j9n_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/fix_channel_token.sh","content":"#!/bin/bash\npython3 << 'PYEOF'\nimport json\n\nwith open('/root/.openclaw/openclaw.json', 'r') as f:\n    config = json.load(f)\n\n# Update channel telegram botToken\nconfig.setdefault('channels', {}).setdefault('telegram', {})['botToken'] = '8644096400:AAG_AqRTg-KtsWKl0EmhnpveJ4RjtMWmiVg'\nconfig['channels']['telegram']['allowFrom'] = ['6053576134']\n\nwith open('/root/.openclaw/openclaw.json', 'w') as f:\n    json.dump(config, f, indent=2)\n\nprint('Done.')\nPYEOF\npkill -9 openclaw 2>/dev/null\nsleep 3\nsystemctl restart openclaw-gateway\necho \"Gateway restarted.\"\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":212,"output":513,"cacheRead":115465,"cacheWrite":288,"totalTokens":116478,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776763691569,"responseId":"0636762da7392a9b4888dd0e94330340"}}
