{"type":"message","id":"7761d72e","parentId":"042ed584","timestamp":"2026-04-21T19:33:33.827Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The session has 1594 lines but the last assistant message doesn't have usage info (the latest message might be a user message). The master-orchestrator session is running and actively managing 43 child subagents. \n\nThe real issue is that the master-orchestrator is managing too many subagents at once (43 subagents in the childSessions list). This is overwhelming the system. The subagent is also experiencing LLM idle timeouts.\n\nThe user wants me to:\n1. Monitor this subagent session\n2. If it stops, signal it to resume\n\nSince the subagent is currently experiencing LLM idle timeout, it's effectively stuck. I should:\n\n\n1. Send a resume signal to the subagent\n2. Or restart it with a fresh context\n\nLet me try sending a message to the subagent directly to wake it up. Actually, the session `52f0c795...` shows `\"status\":\"done\"` which might be stale. Looking at the session history, the subagent was actively sending messages. The issue is the `LLM idle timeout (60s)` error - this means the model stopped responding during a response. I should try sending a wake-up message to the subagent to get it moving again.","thinkingSignature":"c18f15488c374b6223dfce26fcd308b7b6e86606707bb8145bfd4040b92327b5"},{"type":"text","text":"Tình trạng: Context master-orchestrator đã đầy 200K tokens, model xử lý quá chậm → subagent timeout.\n\nGửi signal đánh thức subagent:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_spwlueubxnfj_1","name":"sessions_send","arguments":{"sessionKey":"agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:52f0c795-a0e6-4fbc-9372-fe4cf966a590","message":"Agent này đang bị LLM idle timeout. Kiểm tra context hiện tại - nếu context > 150K tokens thì bắt đầu session mới (không giữ context cũ). Tiếp tục công việc: xây dựng hệ thống PPE Safety Detection System trong version-demo/s1-ppe-safety. Nếu model AHV-Holding-TroLy chậm thì dùng AHV-Holding-DEV. Reply status ngay.","timeoutSeconds":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":92,"output":501,"cacheRead":153874,"cacheWrite":1250,"totalTokens":155717,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776800000485,"responseId":"06370401bcdb4989d64ba027a622c888"}}
