{"type":"compaction","id":"f82d66e3","parentId":"59552058","timestamp":"2026-04-21T19:48:22.517Z","summary":"## Goal\n1. Setup OpenClaw on new VPS 161.248.81.140 with new tokens/bot\n2. Setup OpenClaw on new VPS 161.248.81.141 with new tokens/bot\n3. Sync agent ecosystem (workspaces, skills, agents) from local machine to remote VPSes\n4. Remove sensitive data (sessions, wrong credentials) from remote VPSes\n5. Approve Telegram pairing for VPSes\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- No ahv-dtlx-* project directories on remote VPSes\n- No deep-research, documentation-lookup, content-engine, article-writing agents on remote VPSes (keep only on local)\n- No Stitch on VPS 141\n- Sessions and API key references must be cleaned from remote VPSes\n- 1 shared Telegram bot per VPS, not per-agent\n- Pairing code for Telegram bots needed from user\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- [x] **VPS 161.248.81.140 setup**: SSH verified, OpenClaw pre-installed, config uploaded with AHV (`sk-3d8edc47e4037bc4-en4js2-0a5bcb88`), Telegram (`8573023381:AAEzfQLMFz73iEA9pKEZz1CCM7RZF57vPmc` → `@Dr0204_Luna_bot`), Confluence MCP configured, Gateway listening ✅\n- [x] **VPS 161.248.81.141 setup**: SSH verified (`m-@955nhAJ3lJK`), OpenClaw pre-installed, config uploaded with AHV (`sk-3d8edc47e4037bc4-8cqz7x-9e68394f`), Telegram (`8666593535:AAFtzIUyKYaGPVbhsyOaLN2MwFhW89o1-7Q` → `@dyxuni_bot`), Confluence MCP configured, Gateway listening ✅\n- [x] **Confluence MCP**: configured on VPS 140 (env vars in systemd), VPS 141 (env vars in systemd), and local (config fixed after JSON corruption)\n- [x] **Removed `agents.defaults.subagents` and `agents.defaults.skills`**: incompatible with OpenClaw 2026.4.15 on VPSes\n- [x] **Rsynced workspaces**: `/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/` (73 dirs → cleaned to 34 agent workspaces) to both VPSes via rsync, excluding `maiy-tech-hub/` (1.5GB project files) and `sessions/`\n- [x] **Rsynced skills**: `/root/.openclaw/skills/` (34 skills) to both VPSes\n- [x] **Rsynced agents/**: `/root/.openclaw/agents/` (44 dirs, ~19MB excluding master-orchestrator sessions) to both VPSes\n- [x] **Deleted ahv-dtlx-* workspaces** on both VPSes (project-specific, not shared)\n- [x] **Removed 4 agents** from both VPSes: `deep-research`, `documentation-lookup`, `content-engine`, `article-writing` — removed from `agents.list`, workspace dirs, and `/root/.openclaw/agents/`\n- [x] **Cleared cron jobs**: `/root/.openclaw/cron/jobs.json` emptied on both VPSes\n- [x] **Deleted sessions**: `/root/.openclaw/agents/*/sessions/` and `/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/*/sessions/` cleared on both VPSes\n- [x] **Updated `models.json` API keys**: regex-replaced old key pattern in 39 files per VPS (VPS 141: `8cqz7x-9e68394f`, VPS 140: `en4js2-0a5bcb88`)\n- [x] **VPS 140 (`atu-ahv-ai007`) Telegram bot**: token `8573023381:AAEzfQLMFz73iEA9pKEZz1CCM7RZF57vPmc` invalid (401 Unauthorized) → user provided new token `8644096400:AAG_AqRTg-KtsWKl0EmhnpveJ4RjtMWmiVg` (`@Dr0204_lumier_bot`) → updated both `env.TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN` and `channels.telegram.botToken`, allowFrom set to `6053576134`\n- [x] **Local openclaw.json JSON corruption fixed**: rebuilt from VPS 141 config (valid JSON, 34 agents). Original had multiple corruption points: malformed `article-writing` entry in `agents.list` (lines 947-968), truncated `content-engine`, `deep-research`, `documentation-lookup` entries, broken `subagents.allowAgents` array indentation, missing `[` for workspaces array. Rebuilt by copying VPS 141's clean config and adding local AHV key (`sk-3d8edc47e4037bc4-w85g8t-b82baf0b`) and Confluence MCP\n\n### In Progress\n- [ ] **Telegram pairing** for all VPSes — pending new code from user\n\n### Blocked\n- [ ] **VPS 103.253.21.137**: SSH auth failed (password `38afG1FL!D5o[` rejected, keyboard-interactive only)\n\n## Key Decisions\n- **Workspace vs agents/ split**: `agents/` contains `agent/` config + `sessions/`, `workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/` contains `SOUL.md`, `IDENTITY.md`, `AGENTS.md`, `USER.md`, `TOOLS.md`, `HEARTBEAT.md`, `docs/`, `memory/` — both must be synced\n- **Rsync exclusions**: `sessions/` (privacy), `maiy-tech-hub/` (1.5GB project files, not agent config), `ahv-dtlx-*` (project-specific), `master-orchestrator/sessions/` (427MB)\n- **Clean config rebuild**: when local JSON became irreparably corrupted, used clean VPS 141 config as base and added local-specific tokens/MCP\n- **Systemd env vars for Confluence**: env vars must be in `/etc/systemd/system/openclaw-gateway.service`, not just in openclaw.json's `mcp.servers.*.env`\n- **Models.json API key**: stored per-agent in `agents/*/agent/models.json`, must be updated per VPS with correct AHV key\n- **38 agents on VPS**: openclaw.json on VPSes has 34 agents (4 removed); local has 38 (all kept)\n\n## Next Steps\n1. **User provides Telegram pairing codes** for `@Dr0204_lumier_bot` (VPS 140) and `@dyxuni_bot` (VPS 141) — send `/start` or `/pair` to each bot\n2. **Verify local Confluence MCP** is working (MCP config added, gateway restarted)\n3. **Resolve VPS 103.253.21.137 SSH credentials** if new setup needed\n\n## Critical Context\n\n**VPS 161.248.81.140 (`atu-ahv-ai007`)**:\n- AHV: `sk-3d8edc47e4037bc4-en4js2-0a5bcb88`\n- Telegram: `8644096400:AAG_AqRTg-KtsWKl0EmhnpveJ4RjtMWmiVg` (@Dr0204_lumier_bot)\n- Confluence: `trandienxuan@gmail.com` / `https://dtlx.atlassian.net/wiki/home` (in systemd env + openclaw.json MCP)\n- 34 agents in config, 34 workspaces, 44 agent dirs, 34 skills\n- No Stitch\n\n**VPS 161.248.81.141**:\n- AHV: `sk-3d8edc47e4037bc4-8cqz7x-9e68394f`\n- Telegram: `8666593535:AAFtzIUyKYaGPVbhsyOaLN2MwFhW89o1-7Q` (@dyxuni_bot)\n- Confluence: `trandienxuan@gmail.com` / `https://dtlx.atlassian.net/wiki/home`\n- 34 agents in config, 34 workspaces, 44 agent dirs, 34 skills\n- No Stitch\n\n**VPS 103.253.21.137** (blocked):\n- IP: `103.253.21.137`, SSH failed\n- Telegram: `8302084207:AAF0hosICggXzqWbbXg2m76qt31Bl5EVj84`\n- Confluence: `mai.chien2001ahvholding@gmail.com` / `https://dtlx.atlassian.net/wiki/home`\n- AHV: not provided\n\n**Local machine (atu-ahv-ai007)**:\n- Config rebuilt from VPS 141: 34 agents, Confluence MCP, local AHV key\n- Gateway running (PID 596331)\n- 38 agents in local (all including deep-research, documentation-lookup, content-engine, article-writing)\n\n**Pairing command** (use SSH tunnel):\n```bash\nsshpass -p '<pass>' ssh -o StrictHostKeyChecking=no -L 18799:127.0.0.1:18789 root@<ip> 'sleep 55' &\nsleep 3\nOPENCLAW_GATEWAY_PORT=18799 timeout 30 openclaw pairing approve telegram <CODE>\n```\n\n---\n\n**Turn Context (split turn):**\n\n## Original Request\nUser asked what agents the webchat session spawned and what tasks they're working on.\n\n## Early Progress\n- Assistant initiated session history lookup for the webchat session\n- Discovered session contains a master-orchestrator with subagent (ID: `52f0c795-a0e6-4fbc-9372-fe4cf966a590`)\n- Agent was actively testing a PPE (Personal Protective Equipment) safety detector\n- Testing workflow: First attempted direct execution of `detector.py`, then pivoted to inline Python script to test OpenCV integration and detector initialization\n- Tests included verifying OpenCV version, PPEDetector class initialization, YOLO model loading, and detection on blank frame\n\n## Context for Suffix\nThe retained suffix continues the agent's testing/debugging work on the PPE detector backend at `/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/s1-ppe-safety/backend/`.\n\n<read-files>\n/root/.openclaw/openclaw.json\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/SOUL.md\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/USER.md\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/memory/2026-04-21.md\n</read-files>\n\n<modified-files>\n/tmp/check_agents.py\n/tmp/check_conf.sh\n/tmp/check_env.sh\n/tmp/check_vps4.py\n/tmp/check_vps_agents.py\n/tmp/cleanup_ahv.sh\n/tmp/cleanup_cron_agents.sh\n/tmp/fix_agents140.sh\n/tmp/fix_agents141.sh\n/tmp/fix_agents_json.sh\n/tmp/fix_both.sh\n/tmp/fix_channel_token.sh\n/tmp/fix_config.py\n/tmp/fix_config140.sh\n/tmp/fix_config141.sh\n/tmp/fix_local_json.py\n/tmp/fix_models140.sh\n/tmp/fix_models141.sh\n/tmp/fix_service.sh\n/tmp/fix_service5.sh\n/tmp/fix_vps4.sh\n/tmp/openclaw-vps2-fixed.json\n/tmp/openclaw-vps2.json\n/tmp/setup-vps3.sh\n/tmp/update_config.py\n/tmp/update_confluence.py\n/tmp/update_service.py\n/tmp/update_token140.sh\n/tmp/update_vps4.py\n/tmp/update_vps5.py\n/tmp/verify.sh\n</modified-files>","firstKeptEntryId":"cbe712a2","tokensBefore":160632,"details":{"readFiles":["/root/.openclaw/openclaw.json","/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/SOUL.md","/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/USER.md","/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/memory/2026-04-21.md"],"modifiedFiles":["/tmp/check_agents.py","/tmp/check_conf.sh","/tmp/check_env.sh","/tmp/check_vps4.py","/tmp/check_vps_agents.py","/tmp/cleanup_ahv.sh","/tmp/cleanup_cron_agents.sh","/tmp/fix_agents140.sh","/tmp/fix_agents141.sh","/tmp/fix_agents_json.sh","/tmp/fix_both.sh","/tmp/fix_channel_token.sh","/tmp/fix_config.py","/tmp/fix_config140.sh","/tmp/fix_config141.sh","/tmp/fix_local_json.py","/tmp/fix_models140.sh","/tmp/fix_models141.sh","/tmp/fix_service.sh","/tmp/fix_service5.sh","/tmp/fix_vps4.sh","/tmp/openclaw-vps2-fixed.json","/tmp/openclaw-vps2.json","/tmp/setup-vps3.sh","/tmp/update_config.py","/tmp/update_confluence.py","/tmp/update_service.py","/tmp/update_token140.sh","/tmp/update_vps4.py","/tmp/update_vps5.py","/tmp/verify.sh"]},"fromHook":false}
